  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page resource-detail-page\">\n      <section class=\"section resource-detail-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"resource-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">手冊</p>\n        <h1 id=\"resource-title\">AI 光學分揀系統手冊</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">為評估PET瓶、HDPE瓶、PP及混合可回收塑膠AI識別與光學分揀的團隊提供的產品概述。</p>\n        <div class=\"resource-meta-row\" aria-label=\"資源元資料\">\n          <span>類型：產品手冊</span>\n          <span>更新：2026-06-30</span>\n          <span>買家合身：塑膠回收專案</span>\n          <span>評論時間：10 min</span>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section resource-detail-layout\" aria-labelledby=\"coverage-title\">\n        <article class=\"resource-detail-panel\">\n          <h2 id=\"coverage-title\">本資源涵蓋內容</h2>\n          <ul class=\"feature-list\">\n            <li>典型可回收塑膠原料與分類分類</li>\n            <li>PET、HDPE、PP及混合塑膠分類的系統定位</li>\n            <li>吞吐量、佔地面積與自動化討論重點</li>\n            <li>申請塑膠分揀提案前需準備的問題</li>\n          </ul>\n        </article>\n        <aside class=\"resource-detail-panel\">\n          <h2>何時使用此資源</h2>\n          <p>當你需要比較AI光學分揀與手動分揀或傳統塑膠回收分揀方法時，請使用這本手冊。</p>\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">請求此資源</a>\n        </aside>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\" aria-labelledby=\"related-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">相關資源</p>\n          <h2 id=\"related-title\">規劃塑膠分類專案</h2>\n          <p>在寄送資料前，請先閱讀產品頁面、檢查清單及聯絡表單。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"resource-related-grid\">\n          <a href=\"/products/ai-optical-sorting\">\n            AI 光學分揀產品頁面\n            <span class=\"resource-related-cta\" aria-hidden=\"true\">探索</span>\n          </a>\n          <a href=\"/resources/project-inquiry-checklist\">\n            專案調查檢查清單\n            <span class=\"resource-related-cta\" aria-hidden=\"true\">探索</span>\n          </a>\n          <a href=\"/resources/product-specification-sheet\">\n            產品規格表\n            <span class=\"resource-related-cta\" aria-hidden=\"true\">探索</span>\n          </a>\n          <a href=\"/contact\">\n            傳送 專案 詳情\n            <span class=\"resource-related-cta\" aria-hidden=\"true\">探索</span>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
